            <p facs="#facs_99_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>sont a
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>-1568-
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>[such] as radio, move, and television. There are, in all these things, some elements which one
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>could call cultural goods of the past, which are brought especially in music, and there is much
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>and the information problem leads to these extraordinary things
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>information,
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>answer which, you must "empty your mind
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>like the $100,000-questions, in order to
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>of every meaningful content to take in innumerable facts, and then you might win the $100,000
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>on the basis of this idea! But this is not the worst part of it. A much worse part is the SILENT
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_2_tl_11" n="N011"/>PRODECTION of pretterns of thought which are notselorced, as in totalitarian Iountries, by
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_99_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/> blice power from outside, but which are mediated by the very soft form of taking from you,
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>without any external Cnforcement, many hours of your day, and from children often, all the
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>non- school hours of their day, and what is going on in school under the leading "Bducation for
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>Adjustment" is often not much better—so that from early time on, this patternization is going on.
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>Now here we are before a problem, namely, under these circumstances, is the assistance
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_99_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>against neo-collectivism in this country more possible than in the totalitarian counties? In the
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>totalitariansteries, a resistance is a matter of danger of life. In this country the assistance is a
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>matter of preserning INTERNALLY elements which can be preserved ONLy in the situation of
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>solitude. I can tell you a discussion I had in the business School two months ago, I think it was,
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>about the meaning of business in our time, with very advanced plusents of a special group there;
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>and the final question which I was asked was: "Now if you sum up all what you have told us-
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>means and ends, the creation of means for ends which then themselves
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>about the confusion of
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>Monsieur Mʼaillez lʼhonneur sérieur, et très obéissé
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>Monsieur, il y a été
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>Monsieur
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>de votre beau
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_14" n="N014"/>de votre beau et de
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_15" n="N015"/>Vous avez
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_16" n="N016"/>dʼun autre
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_17" n="N017"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_18" n="N018"/>Vous en
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_19" n="N019"/>dʼavoir lʼautre beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_99_tr_1_tl_20" n="N020"/>cʼest en
